author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
This one is Personal. I discovered Field Music through my friend Nate Wood and I want you to discover them too. 

Link to my Spotify playlist is here: https://open.spotify.com/playlist/1zeMcNwonGBq7JEIi69HC1?si=OIXPVDcYQTeLGeGg3nSb5A&pi=e-0s0bj76YT_iu

Let’s Write A Book - released 2010 from album Field Music (Measure): https://youtu.be/K06H-Zfwq0w?si=1yqpwc2PtypDG68J

Count It Up  - released 2018 from album Open Here: https://youtu.be/9e15OffiGdY?si=REttTXLln1bkFL7h

In Context -  2007 from album Tones of Town: https://youtu.be/DBqx9Tpmj-U?si=bcmDjc7WO4P0sAHx

I Might Have Been Wrong  -  2024 from album Limits of Language: https://youtu.be/C3ecYVmYvRE?si=FBx-hJw1Rs83DpsE

Do Me a Favour  - 2021 from album Flat White Moon: https://youtu.be/ArryWJCgIYM?si=TyqN29B-t7u5CxEJ

Disappointed  -  2016 from album Commontime: https://youtu.be/ttvYmfAnZ30?si=NgBV9lSMIIBLc6wf

title: Thank You For The Field Music
